)

        within group ( order by value )
        over ( partition by table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec )

 as last_first_quartile,
        

    percentile_cont( 
        0.5 )
        within group ( order by value )
        over ( partition by table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec )

 as last_median,
        

    percentile_cont( 
        0.75 )
        within group ( order by value )
        over ( partition by table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec )

 as last_third_quartile
    from
        DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_base_metrics
    where
        time_window_end >
   
    DATEADD('DAY', -30, 
    cast('2024-05-14 00:00:00' as timestamp) 
)

and
        time_window_end <=
    cast('2024-05-15 00:00:00' as timestamp)

    
), abs_deviation as (
    select 
        s.table_name,
        s.column_name,
        s.metric,
        s.interval_length_sec,
        abs( s.value - mv.last_avg ) as absolute_deviation_from_mean,
        abs( s.value - mv.last_median ) as absolute_deviation_from_median
    from
        DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_base_metrics s
    left join 
        median_value mv
        on
            s.table_name = mv.table_name and
            s.column_name = mv.column_name and
            s.metric = mv.metric and
            s.interval_length_sec = mv.interval_length_sec
    where
        s.time_window_end >
   
    DATEADD('DAY', -30, 
    cast('2024-05-14 00:00:00' as timestamp) 
)

and
        s.time_window_end <=
    cast('2024-05-15 00:00:00' as timestamp)
), median_abs_deviation as (
    select distinct
        table_name,
        column_name,
        metric,
        interval_length_sec,
        avg(absolute_deviation_from_mean)  over(partition by table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec)  as mean_absolute_deviation,
        

    percentile_cont( 
        0.5 )
        within group ( order by absolute_deviation_from_median )
        over ( partition by table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec )

 as median_absolute_deviation
    from
        abs_deviation
    
), stats as (
    select
        table_name,
        column_name,
        metric,
        stddev(value) as last_stddev,
        max(time_window_end) as last_metric_time,
        interval_length_sec,
        max(computed_on) as computed_on
    from
        DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_base_metrics
    where
        time_window_end >
   
    DATEADD('DAY', -30, 
    cast('2024-05-14 00:00:00' as timestamp) 
)

and
        time_window_end <=
    cast('2024-05-15 00:00:00' as timestamp)
group by
        table_name, column_name, metric, interval_length_sec
)

select
    s.table_name,
    s.column_name,
    s.metric,
    mv.last_avg,
    s.last_stddev,
    s.last_metric_time,
    s.interval_length_sec,
    s.computed_on,
    mv.last_median,
    mv.last_first_quartile,
    mv.last_third_quartile,
    md.median_absolute_deviation last_median_absolute_deviation,
    md.mean_absolute_deviation last_mean_absolute_deviation
from
    stats s
left join
    median_value mv
    on
        s.table_name = mv.table_name and
        s.column_name = mv.column_name and
        s.metric = mv.metric and
        s.interval_length_sec = mv.interval_length_sec
left join
    median_abs_deviation md
    on 
        s.table_name = md.table_name and
        s.column_name = md.column_name and
        s.metric = md.metric and
        s.interval_length_sec = md.interval_length_sec
select * from DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_base_metrics

with z_score_without_id as (

    select
        stats.table_name as table_name,
        stats.column_name as column_name,
        stats.metric as metric,
        stats.interval_length_sec,
        (last_metric.last_value - stats.last_avg) / (stats.last_stddev + 0.0000000001) as z_score_value,
        case
            when stats.last_median_absolute_deviation = 0 then
                (last_metric.last_value - stats.last_median) / (1.253314 * (stats.last_mean_absolute_deviation + 0.0000000001))
            else
                (0.6745 * (last_metric.last_value - stats.last_median)) / (stats.last_median_absolute_deviation + 0.0000000001) 
        end as modified_z_score_value,
        last_metric.last_value as last_value,
        stats.last_avg as last_avg,
        stats.last_median as last_median,
        stats.last_stddev as last_stddev,
        stats.last_median_absolute_deviation,
        stats.last_mean_absolute_deviation,
        stats.last_third_quartile - stats.last_first_quartile as last_iqr,
        stats.last_first_quartile,
        stats.last_third_quartile,
        
    cast('2024-05-15 00:00:00' as timestamp)
 as time_window_end,
        cast( 
  current_timestamp::timestamp
 as 
    
    TIMESTAMP_NTZ

 ) as computed_on
    from
        DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_last_stats as stats,
        DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_last_metrics as last_metric
    where
        stats.table_name = last_metric.table_name and
        stats.column_name = last_metric.column_name and
        stats.metric = last_metric.metric and
        (
            stats.interval_length_sec = last_metric.interval_length_sec or
            (stats.interval_length_sec is null and last_metric.interval_length_sec is null)
        ) and
        last_metric.last_value is not null and
        stats.last_avg is not null and
        stats.last_stddev is not null
    )

select
    cast (md5(cast(coalesce(cast(table_name as TEXT), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(column_name as TEXT), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(metric as TEXT), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(interval_length_sec as TEXT), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(time_window_end as TEXT), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') as TEXT)) as 
    
    STRING

 ) as id,
    table_name,
    column_name,
    metric,
    z_score_value,
    modified_z_score_value,
    last_value,
    last_avg,
    last_median,
    last_stddev,
    last_median_absolute_deviation,
    last_mean_absolute_deviation,
    last_iqr,
    last_first_quartile,
    last_third_quartile,
    time_window_end,
    interval_length_sec,
    computed_on

from z_score_without_id

select
    z.id,
    z.table_name,
    z.column_name,
    z.metric,
    z.z_score_value,
    z.modified_z_score_value,
    m.anomaly_detector,
    z.last_value,
    z.last_avg,
    z.last_median,
    z.last_stddev,
    z.last_median_absolute_deviation,
    z.last_mean_absolute_deviation,
    z.last_iqr,
    z.last_first_quartile - (cast( 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'whisker_boundary_multiplier' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

 ) * z.last_iqr) lower_bound,
    z.last_third_quartile + (cast( 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'whisker_boundary_multiplier' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

 ) * z.last_iqr) upper_bound,
    z.last_first_quartile,
    z.last_third_quartile,
    z.time_window_end,
    z.interval_length_sec,
    z.computed_on,
    

    case when z.column_name != '' then metric || '(' || column_name || ')'
    else metric
    end 
    || ' is ' ||
    
    
    trim(to_char(
    abs(
        ( 
            cast(last_value - last_avg as 
    
    FLOAT

)
        ) / 
        nullif(
            cast( z.last_avg as 
    
    FLOAT

 )
        , 0) * 100.0
    )
, '9999999999999999990D00'))


    || '% ' ||
    
    case when z.last_value > z.last_avg then 'greater than' 
    when z.last_value = z.last_avg then 'equal to'
    else 'less than' end

    || ' average.'
 as message,
    
    case 
        when z.metric = 'freshness' 
            then cast(
    
    trim(to_char(
    cast(z.last_value as 
    
    FLOAT

) / 3600
, '9999999999999999990D00'))

 as 
    
    STRING

) || ' hours'
        when 
    
    regexp_like(Z.METRIC, 'percent')

 
            then cast(
    
    trim(to_char(z.last_value, '9999999999999999990D00'))

 as 
    
    STRING

) || '%'
        when 
    
    regexp_like(Z.METRIC, 'count')

 
            then cast(z.last_value as 
    
    STRING

)
        else cast(
    
    trim(to_char(z.last_value, '9999999999999999990D00'))

 as 
    
    STRING

)
    end

 as last_value_text
from
    DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_z_score z 
left join DB_DBT_DEMO_101.L3_GOLD.re_data_selected m 
on split_part(

    regexp_replace( table_name, '(")|(`)', ''), '.', 1) = m.database
and split_part(

    regexp_replace( table_name, '(")|(`)', ''), '.', 2) = m.schema
and split_part(

    regexp_replace( table_name, '(")|(`)', ''), '.', 3) = m.name
where
    case when (lower(coalesce(

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'direction' )

, 'both')) = 'up' and z.last_value > z.last_avg)
        or (lower(coalesce(

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'direction' )

, 'both')) = 'down' and z.last_value < z.last_avg)
        or (lower(coalesce(

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'direction' )

, 'both')) != 'up' and lower(coalesce(

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'direction' )

, 'both')) != 'down')
        then
            case 
                when 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'name' )

 = 'z_score' 
                    then abs(z_score_value) > cast(

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'threshold' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

)
                when 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'name' )

 = 'modified_z_score' 
                    then abs(modified_z_score_value) > cast( 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'threshold' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

 )
                when 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'name' )

 = 'boxplot' 
                    then (
                        z.last_value < z.last_first_quartile - (cast( 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'whisker_boundary_multiplier' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

 ) * z.last_iqr)
                        or 
                        z.last_value > z.last_third_quartile + (cast( 

  json_extract_path_text(try_parse_json( m.anomaly_detector ), 'whisker_boundary_multiplier' )

 as 
    
    FLOAT

 ) * z.last_iqr)
                    )
                else false
            end
        else false
    end

select
    'anomaly' as type,
    

    regexp_replace( table_name, '(")|(`)', '') as model,
    message,
    last_value_text as value,
    time_window_end
